    Is Shu Uemura hair oil worth it?
    I wouldn't use it every day, but it's fantastic to use once in a while for extra hydration. It's also a great time saver since you don't need to use conditioner afterwards. The Shu Uemura Essence Absolue line is great. I recommend it if you have dry hair, frizzy hair, or if you just want softer and glossier hair.

    How do you use Shu Uemura hair oil?
    1. To use as a styling aid, apply 1 pump to your hands (a little goes a long way) and work through hair from mid-lengths to ends. 2. To use as a pre-shampoo treatment, use 3-4 pumps and comb into dry hair before shampooing.
